COVID-19 Status 💉 🦠

As of 5:36PM PT today, over 1.4 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 26.5 thousand have died.

In the last day, 390 new infections were reported and 8 deaths. This is trending downwards.

Fortunately, 43.9 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 12 years and older, 79.2% have their 1st shot and 52.7% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is speeding up, but there are 8.1 million doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~19 days for new deliveries to get into arms. At the current rate, all Canadians aged 12+ should have the first dose by Nov-19 and fully vaccinated by Aug-17. There is no approved vaccine for children aged 11 or younger.
